reviews.text: Delicious! Great service. Lovely food. Authentic cuisine. I live across this restaurant and saw that people gave it an overall of 3 stars. What an underestimation! I come here all the time. Don't trust the other reviews! Yours truly, loyal customer

Writing on menu is super duper small.... crazy... who would design such a menu.

Food is ok, fancy presentation on some dishes..... other than that.. nothing to write home about.

I went there for lunch and picked a shanghainese lunch set. Food was good in terms of price/performance. Since the location is a bit remote from business area, it is quite quiet. The setting of the restaurant was comfortable with lots of natural light.

Nice place with tasty Shanghai food. 

Easy to find a table. No waiting is needed most of the time. Price is a little bit high compared with rest of the restaurant nearby, but this worth.

Nice service and hygiene. Good for dinning alone / small group of people. 

Lunch around $70 per person and dinner may be more expensive, depends on how much you order.
Delicious desserts. Good place for afternoon tea.

result.adr_address: 香港沙田銀城街2號
result.name: 置富第一城 ‧ 樂薈

reviews.text: 環境頗舒通，但食肆質素一般，時装及地産商鋪太多.缺乏吸引力.

新界沙田第一城是大型屋苑，包括兩部分的商場; 置富第一城商場和置富第一城·樂薈商場(前稱銀城商場)。兩個商塲都設有客户中心，希望為城區內的顧客提供「以客為本」的服務。樂薈商場地方清潔，有琳琅滿目的店鋪; 包括酒樓、快餐店、麵包/西餅店、超級市場、銀行、電器舖、髮廊，洗衣店等等，為第一城居民提供各式各類的服務和選擇。屋苑有游泳池、天台花園、多層停車場。在置富第一城·樂薈地下有多間地產代理公司、living plaza、JHC、一粥麵、速遞、食品店和上海店等。
在第一城居住生活的住客，有两个商场，生活很方便。
很舒服購買的 Shopping Mall.
